Q17: To submit the claim, ensure prior authorization is obtained through the UnitedHealthcare Provider Portal. The ordering provider should complete the prior authorization process online or by phone. Laboratories must register their tests in the UnitedHealthcare Genetic Test Registry to participate in the genetic and molecular testing prior authorization process. For detailed instructions, refer to the Genetic and Molecular Testing Prior Authorization and Advance Notification Guide available on the UnitedHealthcare provider website.
